OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEarly years sector joins   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcall for Ofsted changes    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Early Years Alliance charity, which
OL,6, represents nurseries, preschools and   
OL,7, childminders, wants a review of the    
OL,8, grades given by Ofsted inspectors.     
OL,10,FThe charity took a snapshot survey of  
OL,11,Fearly years' staff, which revealed many
OL,12,Fof them found inspections stressful.   
OL,14,FOfsted says it knows "inspections can  
OL,15,Fbe challenging", and wants them to be  
OL,16,F"as constructive as possible".         
OL,18,FTeaching unions have called for        
OL,19,Finspections to be paused after head    
OL,20,Fteacher Ruth Perry took her own life.  
